function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

@header('Content-Type: text/plain');

chdir(__DIR__);
$cont = @file_get_contents('changelog.json.php');
if ($cont === false) err('Cannot read changelog.json.php');
$json = @json_decode($cont, true);
if ($json === null) err('Cannot parse changelog.json.php');
$latest_version = false;
foreach ($json as $v) {
	if (isset($v['version']) && (substr($v['version'], -4) != '-dev')) {
		$latest_version = $v['version'];
		break; // the first item is the latest version
	}
}
if ($latest_version != '2.0.2.2') err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.2.2!');

if (version_compare(PHP_VERSION, '7.4.0') < 0) {
	err('You need at least PHP Version 7.4 to update to this version');
}

if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: changelog.json.php');
	writefile_1();
	if (!is_file('changelog.json.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): changelog.json.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('changelog.json.php') != '428689f4d46902cae9eb6f70c73a3fedc7161c10') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('changelog.json.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of changelog.json.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '428689f4d46902cae9eb6f70c73a3fedc7161c10') {
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '5a7e3b9b5b0e6762ac17003b8aedbe40ca83e091') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: changelog.json.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('changelog.json.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('changelog.json.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('changelog.json.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_1();
		if (@sha1_file('changelog.json.php') !== '428689f4d46902cae9eb6f70c73a3fedc7161c10') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): changelog.json.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	writefile_2();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') != '943bbf8ade9eec87012ca395102f8fdee33b53c7') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '943bbf8ade9eec87012ca395102f8fdee33b53c7') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '2a284aff991a51cd231057ee8eccb615ffe2925d') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_2();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '943bbf8ade9eec87012ca395102f8fdee33b53c7') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
	writefile_3();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php') != 'c3ba2e41f940ee0064d2cbb38df837bc697df444') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php') !== 'c3ba2e41f940ee0064d2cbb38df837bc697df444') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php') !== '1e404514bcb6cb1ab06b10af8feefe84b459f9d4') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_3();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php') !== 'c3ba2e41f940ee0064d2cbb38df837bc697df444') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusGui.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('oidplus.min.css.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: oidplus.min.css.php');
	writefile_4();
	if (!is_file('oidplus.min.css.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): oidplus.min.css.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('oidplus.min.css.php') != 'd90df04a122be8b1d358e12334a2298072c01d32') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): oidplus.min.css.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('oidplus.min.css.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of oidplus.min.css.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.css.php') !== 'd90df04a122be8b1d358e12334a2298072c01d32') {
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.css.php') !== '27267aee6b3bcb57faa848c59317b6401cbad562') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: oidplus.min.css.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('oidplus.min.css.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('oidplus.min.css.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('oidplus.min.css.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_4();
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.css.php') !== 'd90df04a122be8b1d358e12334a2298072c01d32') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): oidplus.min.css.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('oidplus.min.js.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: oidplus.min.js.php');
	writefile_5();
	if (!is_file('oidplus.min.js.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): oidplus.min.js.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') != '0daf2ff4c47fb5f6fcb18aa4a06b4df676cf9064') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): oidplus.min.js.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('oidplus.min.js.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of oidplus.min.js.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') !== '0daf2ff4c47fb5f6fcb18aa4a06b4df676cf9064') {
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') !== '65c958c6cf9a3b257852e0cf0a5a98a39bca7ebf') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: oidplus.min.js.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('oidplus.min.js.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('oidplus.min.js.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('oidplus.min.js.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_5();
		if (@sha1_file('oidplus.min.js.php') !== '0daf2ff4c47fb5f6fcb18aa4a06b4df676cf9064') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): oidplus.min.js.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js');
	writefile_6();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js') != '2a7594a439b35d29491277dfc1b8cfc2bad8c62f') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js') !== '2a7594a439b35d29491277dfc1b8cfc2bad8c62f') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js') !== '2b0cc786e5d9905cdf344f2c3680626ea3e99d57') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js');

			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_6();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js') !== '2a7594a439b35d29491277dfc1b8cfc2bad8c62f') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js');
